Returns
a kernel bundle in state State which contains all of the device images that are compatible with at least one of the devices in Devs, further filtered to contain only those device images that contain kernels with the given identifiers. These identifiers may represent kernels that are defined in the application, device built-in kernels, or a mixture of the two. The bundles set of associated devices is Devs.
